data.description: This cozy (adorable), well-lit 1950's home with original wood floors and details offers many upgrades and a small fenced yard.  Recently updated kitchen with new cabinets & flooring.  New A/C unit in 2021.  Roof was replaced in 2022 with a warranty.   Home is energy efficient with insulation added in 2022.  Gutters feature leaf guards.  Wash/dyer (newer), stove and refrigerator in 2021 are included.  Property has been well maintained for its age.  Offered AS-IS.  Buyer pays all closing costs.  Owner will provide concessions for needed repairs as negotiated prior to signing of purchase contract.
